<h2>Photo Albums</h2>

<p>Thank you everyone for coming and making our special day so awesome! If you took pictures, please share them with us here.</p>

<p>&mdash; Amiel and Hallie</p>

<% if @tags.size > 0 then %>
	<ul class="thumbnails">
		<%= render @tags %>
	</ul>
<% else %>

	<div class="no-content">Unfortunately, nobody's uploaded any photos yet. Why not <%=link_to 'upload your own?', new_photo_path %></div>

<% end %>                                 
<%= link_to 'Add Your Photos', new_photo_path, class: 'button' %>